694
00:48:10,345 --> 00:48:11,888
Ini amaran terakhir saya.

695
00:48:11,972 --> 00:48:13,432
Tolong, pergi sahaja.

696
00:48:14,182 --> 00:48:16,018
Sayang, mari sini!

697
00:48:16,101 --> 00:48:17,561
Ya, puan!

698
00:48:17,644 --> 00:48:18,854
