825
00:56:18,875 --> 00:56:22,420
Awak betul-betul bertekad
nak heret Cik Song jatuh ke?

826
00:56:27,300 --> 00:56:28,301
Kesian Cik Song.

827
00:56:29,594 --> 00:56:31,971
Kau memang kejam. Alamak.

828
00:56:38,103 --> 00:56:40,146
HIT HOMESHOPPING
DAM YE-JIN

829
00:56:55,495 --> 00:56:58,706
Mu-won, mari kita tamatkan hubungan
