Kau siapa untuk halang dia?

878
00:59:48,459 --> 00:59:49,460
Maafkan saya.

879
00:59:54,465 --> 00:59:55,550
Saya betul-betul minta maaf.

880
01:00:11,149 --> 01:00:12,150
Maaf.

881
01:00:15,236 --> 01:00:16,529
Saya betul-betul minta maaf.

